 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/879/is-posible-to-minimize-a-window/?answer=881#post-id-881</link><description>This is not possible.</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Dec 2012 11:02:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/879/is-posible-to-minimize-a-window/?answer=881#post-id-881</guid></item></channel></rss>